# System packages required by the Rust build of mediaflow-proxy-light.
# boring-sys2 (via rquest -> extractors) statically compiles BoringSSL using
# bindgen + cmake + ninja, which needs:
#   * clang + libclang-dev  — bindgen FFI generation
#   * cmake + ninja-build   — BoringSSL build system
#   * golang-go             — BoringSSL's boringssl.go fetches
#   * perl                  — openssl-style generated source headers
# Heroku-24 base image already provides: build-essential, git, python3, pkg-config.
clang
libclang-dev
cmake
ninja-build
golang-go
perl
